1. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper proposes a new measurement noise model for angle-of-arrival (AOA) positioning, which can be considered as a signal processing problem. 
2. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The proposed VMF measurement noise model based filters can be seen as a control system for improving the accuracy of AOA positioning. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses computer simulations to compare the performance of different algorithms, which can be considered as a machine learning task. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): AOA positioning is an important technique for wireless communication systems, and the paper may be relevant to this field. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): AOA positioning can also be used in computer vision applications, such as object tracking and localization.
